{"tid":54733,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本] 7日6夜一月名古屋行程求評","createTime":"2016-12-25T18:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T05:57:10.000Z","uid":45870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cccdc2a9d3adcabe782f4205af83a16f9c457d86","tid":54733,"uid":45870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:52:35.000Z","msg":"黎緊同四個朋友去名古屋名古屋玩，但係交通上有好大問題<br />\n因為我book唔到白川鄉來回金澤嘅巴士，搞到要用貴啲嘅北陸JR pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要高山&gt;&gt;白川鄉&gt;&gt;新高岡&gt;&gt;金澤咁行，想問下仲有無其它方法可以執下個行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1(31/12): 1245 到中部機場&gt;&gt; 榮區 &gt;&gt; 熱田神宮 (宿名古屋栄)<br />\n<br />\n想問下過年名古屋有咩活動?熱田神宮係咪多人到行唔到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 2(1/1): 因為間酒店無得取消所以要stay係名古屋兩日，但係市內又無咩景點好去(因為我地唔鐘意Shopping<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )...請問有無咩地方好推介?<br />\n<br />\nDay 3(2/1): check out 名古屋 &gt;&gt; 高山 &gt;&gt; 白川鄉 &gt;&gt; 新高岡 &gt;&gt; 金澤 (宿金澤airbnb)<br />\nDay 4(3/1): check out 金澤市內景點 &gt;&gt; 加賀温泉 (宿加賀温泉)<br />\n<br />\n第四日其實可以唔去加賀返去高山到住，但係就用唔晒張JR pass，加賀温泉值唔值得去?<br />\n<br />\nDay 5(4/1): check out 加賀温泉 &gt;&gt; 金澤 &gt;&gt; 富山 &gt;&gt; 高山 &gt;&gt; 新穗高温泉 (宿新穗高温泉)<br />\n<br />\n依日就好似全日都係搭車咁<br />\n<br />\nDay 6(5/1): check out 新穗高纜車 &gt;&gt; 高山 &gt;&gt;下呂 (宿下呂)<br />\nDay 7(6/1): 下呂 &gt;&gt; 名古屋 &gt;&gt; 1325機返香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔去加賀温泉，day 3 直接去金澤玩，day 4 係金澤玩完再返高山住，day 5 高山去白川鄉再返新穗高温泉<br />\n咁樣會唔會好好多，因為唔想行程好趕，而且係金澤都多啲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127e22d254bb9b0989090ab4f136420fd19c4965","tid":54733,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:56:20.000Z","msg":"未去過 我都想搵人同我去"},{"pid":"c6d536b0fefb528913b435156159d9e1f0fd96fa","tid":54733,"uid":68696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T19:28:25.000Z","msg":"去名古屋唔去立山黑部 等於無去<br />\n不過依家封緊山"},{"pid":"8ea025a16df34e7fa2c5257df53f8fc1f83dcad8","tid":54733,"uid":5782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去名古屋唔去立山黑部 等於無去<br />\n不過依家封緊山</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔封山個陣都要返學，我都想去"},{"pid":"ae43b3266af812aaf8d4f3b1ef0ac43b8c4f5ac9","tid":54733,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"245ce536d14b192ad7a7cf2d512dfe2e05b7d40f","tid":54733,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"第2日check下名古屋百貨排福袋<br />\n記得食饅魚飯 好撚好食"},{"pid":"2582c62e1bd7b90230f0306742099e7cc0315a47","tid":54733,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"唔買野 市區都應該冇野行啦 但名古屋都幾多好野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://travel.ettoday.net/article/658890.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ettoday.net%2Farticle%2F658890.htm&d=skPcRPOHki9g%2B54DNKJBamN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=7e39bf51\" target=\"_blank\">http://travel.ettoday.net/article/658890.htm</a><br />\nCheck下呢個睇下岩唔岩 不過唔知1月1有冇開"},{"pid":"b762a3f80106266539562ab1ec1b2b1d7b2e0c6f","tid":54733,"uid":6495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:16:28.000Z","msg":"一句講哂<br />\n如果你為左用盡你張pass而去改行程/兜黎兜去 <br />\n係一件好on9既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb76bbb10fea6d46f0bee8e51ad6902ca8c18e2","tid":54733,"uid":26622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:00:51.000Z","msg":"香港一名古屋一下呂一高山一白川郷一金澤一名古屋一香港"},{"pid":"33db7431b64adc385963f07ce4237982e2f91eef","tid":54733,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"果時book咗去白川鄉巴士<br />\n<br />\n去到個姐姐同我講早一班有空位上唔上<br />\n<br />\n先知原來唔洗book都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480625af6b4362dfe034dc382dd3b3f9d1e5f733","tid":54733,"uid":36667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"去名古屋，一定要去愛地球博記念公園，近郊風景好好，仲有得參觀龍貓個屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}